    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚总理在总统选举前的民意调查中保持领先</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/romanian-premier-keeps-lead-in-poll-ahead-of-presidential-ballot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项民意调查显示，罗马尼亚总理马塞尔·乔拉库有望在下周的总统选举第一轮中获胜，并可能与极端民族主义政党的领导人进行决选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/romanian-premier-keeps-lead-in-poll-ahead-of-presidential-ballot</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 11:56:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞称检察官试图阻止法国选民的选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/le-pen-says-prosecutors-are-trying-to-block-french-voter-options</link>
      <description><![CDATA[极右翼领导人玛丽娜·勒庞指责法国检察官干涉民主进程，并呼吁禁止她参加下届总统选举。]]></description>
